        <num>CCP 8</num>
        <heading>8.  Jurisdiction over property; in rem</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 8.  Jurisdiction over property; in rem
A court which is otherwise competent under the laws of this state has jurisdiction to enforce a right in, to, or against property having a situs in this state, claimed or owned by a nonresident.</p>
        </content>
